OL,3,CNigerian chess champion breaks
OL,4,Cmarathon record by playing for 60 hours
OL,6,Fchess champion and child education
OL,7,Fadvocate Tunde Onakoya has broken the
OL,8,Frecord for the longest chess marathon
OL,9,Fafter playing for 60 hours nonstop
OL,10,Funder the bright lights of 's Times
OL,11,FSquare.
OL,13,FGuinness World Records has not yet
OL,14,Fconfirmed Onakoya's attempt, which can
OL,15,Fsometimes take weeks, but for many
OL,16,FNigerians, the 29-year-old is already
OL,17,Fconsidered something of a national
OL,18,Fhero.
