OL,3,CNigerian chess champion breaks
OL,4,Cmarathon record by playing for 60 hours
OL,6,FOnakoya is attempting to raise $1
OL,7,Fmillion for a charity to support
OL,8,Feducation for children across Africa.
OL,10,FHe had aimed to play for 58 hours but
OL,11,Fcontinued until hitting the 60-hour
OL,12,Fmark in the early hours of Saturday
OL,13,Fmorning, surpassing the previous
OL,14,Frecord of 56 hours, 9 minutes and 37
OL,15,Fseconds set in 2018 by Hallvard Haug
OL,16,FFlatebo and Sjur Ferkingstad of Norway.
