OL,3,CNigerian chess champion breaks
OL,4,Cmarathon record by playing for 60 hours
OL,6,FAmong those who came out to cheer him
OL,7,Fon in Manhattan were Nigerian
OL,8,FAfrobeats superstar Davido and singer
OL,9,FAdekunle Gold.
OL,11,FNigeria's President Bola Tinubu was
OL,12,Famong those who congratulated Onakoya
OL,13,Fonline, praising him for "setting a
OL,14,Fnew world chess record and sounding
OL,15,Fthe gong of Nigeria's resilience, self-
OL,16,Fbelief, and ingenuity at the square of
OL,17,Fglobal acclaim."
